2460	FREDERICK THE GREAT	In this biography of Frederick the Great, Nancy Mitford carefully unravels the complex character of one of Europe's brilliant rulers. She re-creates his unhappy youth; his reforming zeal, which paved the way for a united Germany; and his spectacular wars.	224	1970	\N	\N	9780140036534	https://images.gr-assets.com/books/1461614488m/50726.jpg
